# Patch 135R moves this generic repair block before the main() call so the command
# dispatcher can resolve the functions at runtime. It keeps Patch 135 behavior.
# This patch is intentionally generic. It converts the latest import/path probe
# result into a repair-evidence packet, then calls the local LLM through fixed
# Ollama argv to draft a repair proposal. It writes Forge memory reports only.
# It cannot edit project files, engine files, ledgers, Chroma, or apply patches.
import json as _p135_json
