        "next_patch": next_patch,
        "recommended_next_patch": next_patch,
        "plain_english": "Forge now has a roadmap-grounded build sequence. Stuck repairs are tracked as deferred work instead of hijacking the whole roadmap." if clean else "Forge build sequence exists, but the verified state is not clean enough to continue.",
